<chapter version="1.2.0" number="14" name="Choosing Home">
  <summary>
    Formal acknowledgment: Kira could signal for faster rescue through isolation. She CHOOSES to stay. Not stuck - choosing. The plants welcome her not as guest or crisis, but as family. Looking ahead: challenges yes, but also discoveries, relationships, life. "This isn't the adventure I imagined. It's better." Standing at the beginning of 10 years together, ready.
  </summary>
  <focus>
    Choice as triumph. Kira realizes what Mav never found - belonging, presence, home. Found family celebrated. "The universe rewards those who show up." Open ending: not resolved, but ready and together.
